# 0.2.1 (2018-10-15)

- Bugfix: Registration object is now correctly URI-encoded

# 0.2.0 (2017-09-07)

- Conferences are now loaded via AJAX instead of being hard-coded
- Now features a password-protected questionnaire editor
- Route /conference/<name> is now /<name>
- CaptionsItems and captions in other items allow HTML and line breaks
- The backend is now no longer in this codebase
- Updated dependencies and re-structured some code

# 0.1.0 (2017-01-15)

- Updated dependencies
-- angular to 2.3.1 (from angular2-rc.4)
-- angular-cli to 1.0.0-beta.24 (from 1.0.0-beta.1)
-- dropped systemjs in favor of webpack
-- angular-material to 2.0.0-beta.1 (from alpha.6)

# 0.0.6 (2016-08-09)

- Added mail function (testing)

# 0.0.5 (2016-07-29)

- Updated angular from 2.0.0-rc.1 to rc.4
- Updated angular router
- Updated angular-material2 from alpha.4 to alpha.6
- Changed SingleChoiceItem interface
- Changed cache control

# 0.0.4 (2016-05-16)

- QuickFix: Status returned by server was ignored

# 0.0.3 (2016-05-16)

- Changed text displayed while loading
- Fixed radio buttons
- Registration is now saved via a server-side PHP script

# 0.0.2 (2016-05-11)

- Registration form gathers data as object now
- Scrollable design
- Radio buttons do work
- Link items
- Back button that navigates from registration to list
- Changed JSON schema for conferences

# 0.0.1 (2016-05-10)

- Initial version
- Can only render hard-coded conferences
- No server communication
